        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *moderate reinforcing steel shield* (Hardness 8, HP 84, BT 42) has an image of a cinder dragon\u2019s head painted on it. Additional metal adornments accentuate the fearsome mouth.",
