                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You Raise your Shield and Stride up to twice your Speed in a straight line. You can move through creatures with this movement, but you can\u2019t end your movement in their space. Creatures you moved through take 5d8 fire damage (DC 31 basic Reflex save). Creatures who critically fail also take 1d8 persistent fire damage.",
